title: Study of Galatians 4 led by Luis Menéndez-Antuña
time: '7:30 PM Eastern Time'
series: lenten-detox
---
In this session, Dr. Luis Menéndez-Antuña will explore [Galatians chapter 4](https://bible.oremus.org/?ql=512375942), with a focus on the Allegory of Hagar and Sarah, and unpack its use in the justification and perpetuation of slavery and racism.

